Interface FStringConstant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FConstant, FExpression, FInitializerExpression, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FStringConstantImpl

    public interface FStringConstant
extends FConstant
    A representation of the model object 'FString Constant'. This class represents strings constants in the Franca contract action language.

    The following features are supported:

    • Val
